ril de 2016}}</ref>\n! width=\"20\"| <small>[[Billboard 200|US]]<br /><ref name=\"billboard2\">{{citar web |titulo=Alessia Cara - Chart history \u2013 Billboard 200 (US) |url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/6592648/Alessia+Cara/chart?f=305 |publicado=Billboard.com |acessodata=22 de outubro de 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Know-It-All]]''\n* Released: November 13, 2015\n* Label: [[Def Jam Recordings|Def Jam]]\n* Format: [[Compact disc|CD]], Download digital\n|align=\"center\"| 8\n|align=\"center\"| 16\n|align=\"center\"| 19\n|align=\"center\"| 99\n|align=\"center\"| 52\n|align=\"center\"| 34\n|align=\"center\"| 26\n|align=\"center\"| 21\n|align=\"center\"| 14\n|align=\"center\"| 9\n|\n* {{USA}}:      1 000 000\n* {{CAN}}:      100 000\n|\n* {{USA}}: {{Certification|silver}}<ref name=\"RIAA\">{{citar web |url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&se=Alessia+Cara#search_section |titulo=RIAA \u2013 Alessia Cara |publicado=[[Recording Industry Association of America]] |data=22 de maio de 2017 |acessodata=30 de maio de 2017}}</ref>\n* {{CAN}}: {{Certification|silver}}<ref name=\"MC\">{{citar web |url=https://musiccanada.com/gold-platinum/?fwp_gp_search=Alessia%20Cara |titulo=Gold/Platinum - Music Canada |publicado=[[Music Canada]] |acessodata=31 de julho de 2017}}</ref>\n* {{DNK}}: {{Certification|Gold}}<ref>{{citar web |url=http://ifpi.dk/?q=content/alessia-cara-know-it-all |titulo=Alessia Cara \"Know-It-All\" |publicado=[[IFPI Denmark]] |data=21 de mar\u00e7o de 2017 |acessodata=28 de mar\u00e7o de 2017 |l\u00edngua=da}}</ref>\n* {{UK}}: {{Certification|Silver}}\n|-\n| ''[[The Pains of Growing]]''\n* Released: November 30, 2018\n* Label: [[Def Jam Recordings|Def Jam]]\n* Format: [[Compact disc|CD]], Download digital\n|align=\"center\"| 21\n|align=\"center\"| 76\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|align=\"center\"| 78\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|align=\"center\"| \u2014\n|align=\"